data.description: Discover a stunning 5-bed, 4.5-bath home in Grande View Estates, NEW roof/HVAC. This all-brick, 3-level residence spans 4,000 sq ft, featuring a sprinkler-equipped yard and a 3-car garage. The main level offers a dining room, laundry, gas-lit fireplace in the living room, and a sleek kitchen with an island. The main floor primary suite includes a shower, jacuzzi tub, and walk-in closet. Upstairs, find 3 beds, 2 baths, and a bonus room. The finished basement features a bedroom, full bath, media room, and office. Enjoy private access to a trail from the backyard. Close to Alabaster schools, a clubhouse, pool, and tennis courts. Book a tour today!
